=========================================================
Interview One-Liner
=========================================================

StringBuffer:
"Use StringBuffer when multiple threads access the same object because it is synchronized and thread-safe."

StringBuilder:
"Use StringBuilder when only one thread accesses the object because it is faster and not synchronized."

